cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "MCP Explorer"
abstract: >
  MCP Explorer is an open-source web application for exploring and interacting
  with Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers. It provides a Vue 3 + PrimeVue
  frontend backed by an ASP.NET Core 10 API, supporting multiple transport
  types (SSE, Streamable HTTP, stdio), connection management with Azure Key Vault
  secret resolution, Entra ID / OAuth authentication, AI-assisted tool invocation,
  workflow automation, and an elicitation dialog system. Deployable as a single
  container or as separate services via Docker Compose.
